                <h1>What Is Social Advertising?</h1>
                <img src="assets/socmedia.jpg" class='img-fluid' /><br>
                <br>
                <p class="black">Social advertising is the process of creating and deploying clickable ads to reach target audiences. 
                    You can reach them through social media platforms, messaging apps, news feeds, and even outside apps and websites. 
                    Companies use social advertising campaigns to build brand awareness, generate leads, 
                    and/or capture sales revenue.There are many social advertising channels available but the ones that 
                    will be mostly focused here are:</p><br>
                    <br>

                <img src="assets/google.jpg" class='img-fluid' /><br>
